gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pelicans 141, Warriors 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pelicans defeat the Warriors, 141-105. Jonas Valanciunas led New Orleans with 21 points and nine rebounds as Zion Williamson (19 points, five rebounds, seven assists) and Trey Murphy III (16 points, four rebounds, six assists) totaled 35 points. Moses Moody led the Warriors with 21 points as Trayce Jackson-Davis added a career-high 19 points. The Pelicans have now won six of their last seven games (4-1 in January) to improve to 23-15, as the Warriors move to 17-20.
